<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 21:12:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英国立法者传唤 Shein 和 Temu 询问其劳工行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-summon-shein-temu-questioning-over-labour-practices-2025-01-02/</link><description>希望在伦敦上市的快时尚在线零售商 Shein 将于 1 月 7 日在英国举行听证会，英国议会委员会计划就这家 2008 年在中国成立的公司供应链中工人的权利提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 17:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-summon-shein-temu-questioning-over-labour-practices-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国提议进一步限制电池、关键矿产技术的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-proposes-further-export-curbs-battery-critical-minerals-tech-2025-01-02/</link><description>周四发布的一份文件显示，中国商务部已提议对一些用于制造电池组件和加工关键矿物锂和镓的技术实施出口限制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 15:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-proposes-further-export-curbs-battery-critical-minerals-tech-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于激励措施未能刺激需求，特斯拉年度交付量首次下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-posts-first-fall-annual-deliveries-demand-slows-2025-01-02/</link><description>特斯拉周四公布年度交付量首次下降，原因是这家埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)领导的电动汽车制造商的老化产品线提供了丰厚的年终激励措施，而新款 Cyber​​truck 皮卡未能吸引对高借贷成本保持警惕的客户。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 14:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-posts-first-fall-annual-deliveries-demand-slows-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>钴矿商 Jervois 达成救援协议以更好地与中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cobalt-miner-jervois-rescue-deal-after-struggle-compete-with-china-2025-01-02/</link><description>钴矿商 Jervois Global 周四表示，作为预先计划的破产程序的一部分，其一家贷方将将该公司私有化，这是随着中国竞争加剧而努力生存的最新一家西方矿商。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 13:07:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cobalt-miner-jervois-rescue-deal-after-struggle-compete-with-china-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车在挪威获得市场份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicles-gain-market-share-norway-2025-01-02/</link><description>挪威道路联合会 (OFV) 周四的数据显示，仅五年时间，中国电动汽车就已飙升至挪威新车销量的近 10%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 11:46:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicles-gain-market-share-norway-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：今年第一个交易日，需谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-02/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 11:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑制定限制或禁止中国无人机的潜在规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</link><description>美国商务部周四表示，正在考虑制定新规则，对中国无人机实施限制，以国家安全考虑为由限制或禁止中国无人机在美国销售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 10:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>价格战进入第三年，中国电动汽车制造商扩大购买激励措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-extend-buying-incentives-price-war-enters-third-year-2025-01-02/</link><description>随着全球最大汽车市场的价格战持续第三年，包括蔚来汽车和理想汽车在内的中国电动汽车制造商效仿市场领导者特斯拉和比亚迪，将购买激励措施延长至 2025 年初。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 10:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-extend-buying-incentives-price-war-enters-third-year-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国将28家美国实体列入出口管制名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adds-28-us-entities-export-control-list-2025-01-02/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国已将 28 家美国实体列入出口管制清单，以“维护国家安全和利益”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 08:21:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adds-28-us-entities-export-control-list-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>随着竞争加剧，苹果在中国提供 iPhone 折扣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-discounts-china-competition-intensifies-2025-01-02/</link><description>苹果公司在中国为其最新款 iPhone 机型提供罕见的最高 500 元人民币的折扣，这家美国科技巨头正在采取行动，抵御来自华为等国内竞争对手日益激烈的竞争，以捍卫自己的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-discounts-china-competition-intensifies-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫健委将缩小精神卫生服务差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</link><description>中国国家卫生健康委员会表示，随着当局努力解决越来越多的心理健康问题，特别是儿童和青少年的心理健康问题，将在2025年至2027年期间解决心理健康服务方面的差距。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道新年首次中国“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-chinese-combat-patrol-new-year-2025-01-02/</link><description>在台湾总统赖清德再次表示愿意与北京对话后，台湾国防部周四表示，中国战机和军舰已进行新年首次环岛“战斗巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-chinese-combat-patrol-new-year-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普2.0风险加剧，欧洲、亚洲和美国工厂2024年末表现疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asias-factories-end-2024-weak-footing-trump-20-risks-mount-2025-01-02/</link><description>亚洲、欧洲和美国的工厂活动在 2024 年结束时表现疲软，原因是唐纳德·特朗普连任总统导致贸易风险不断加大，加上中国经济复苏脆弱，新年预期恶化。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 03:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asias-factories-end-2024-weak-footing-trump-20-risks-mount-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国工厂活动增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/growth-chinas-factory-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-01-02/</link><description>周四的一项私营部门调查显示，由于对贸易前景的担忧导致出口订单下降，整体销售受到抑制，中国12月份工厂活动有所增长，但增速低于预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 01:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/growth-chinas-factory-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>随着投资者假期归来，油价因中国乐观情绪而稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-investors-return-holidays-eye-china-recovery-2025-01-02/</link><description>周四，随着投资者在习近平主席承诺促进增长后对中国经济和燃料需求持乐观态度，在 2025 年第一个交易日回归，油价每桶上涨逾 1 美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 01:34:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-investors-return-holidays-eye-china-recovery-2025-01-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>